      "title": "A vegetable and fruit train from Hali Canal to Fort",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe said that as a pilot project, a freight train will be run from Hali Canal to Colombo Fort.",
        "The President mentioned that this step is being taken to ensure the preservation of their freshness and 200 million rupees will be allocated for the provision of facilities for this purpose."
      ],
